Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}炎发灼眼的讨伐者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(彻底解决)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…就已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的我和阿拉斯拖鲁会解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮他找到完美无缺的火焰之雾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是留下男人而死去的女人最后的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  比鲁海尔米娜 提亚玛特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你们拥有天下无敌的好运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「千征令」奥尔贡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经让炎发灼眼的讨伐者订下契约了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎发灼眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  在她习惯这个世界的这期间里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不可以让你逃走是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既非炎发灼眼的讨伐者也非我是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彩…彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「彩虹之翼」梅利希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的誓言 重要的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果手下留情的话可伤脑筋了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我先练练手…的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了呢 千征令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙你关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要测试我「虹天剑」的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比你更适合的人选了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  马上结束它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,订下契约时的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这契约并不是什么命运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样我还是要自己选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要想办法从这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要与强者交手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量正涌出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…这就是火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是赌上生死的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是传说中的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该也有什么弱点的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点就能破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:07:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是「夜笠」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎发灼眼的讨伐者所穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我翅膀的一部分化成的黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…以赐予强者武具为使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我自愿成为密司提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说人类自己成为密司提斯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…寻求与其相称之强者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…自愿成为密司提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是指那把大太刀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…铠甲武士「天目一个」和大太刀「贽殿遮那」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有制作这些的刀匠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎这三个人格混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:09:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赐予超越人类的强者注入我生命精华的武具——贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为寻求与之相称的强者  自愿成为密司提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了寻找那个强者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心甘情愿舍弃作为人的一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也和我一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以自己的意志 来寻找自己的归属
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一心一意的前进着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将成为你主人的强者…就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到了这会儿 就不必说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比鲁海尔米娜·卡卢梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我只是为了完成与她的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而苟活到现在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么乱来的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真担心刚刚得到的火焰之雾就这么失去了也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常清楚只是偶然成功的罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比锻炼还艰苦一百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比红世之徒还可怕…一千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然说了  就要负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…看来好像某个家伙被干掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了大规模的崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉是…红世的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小白…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 阿拉斯拖鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢的人可以随意处置对方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不像是对所迷上的女人提出的条件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有三条约定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准再吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在扰乱世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能的锻炼在我之后出现的炎发灼眼的讨伐者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的决战  虽然很艰苦但尽兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「彩虹之翼」梅利希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见你啊…炎发灼眼的讨伐者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比鲁海尔米娜·卡卢梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想一下我们现在身处此地的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来实现她的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…大概只是为了这个…而在一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个彻彻底底…令人讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正见证着新时代的来临是也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…新的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天目一个的力量就只有大太刀而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个不应使用自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而以格斗去迎战的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我们红世之徒对战时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光从表面的攻击来判断战斗方式是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外表运动的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要感觉内部存在之力的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是察觉自在法的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对外观的警戒也不能放松
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  必须记住的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们红世之徒所操纵的自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是会引起任何不可能发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊慌没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意现实存在的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为我们的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和红世有关的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该闭嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比鲁海尔米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了新时代的来临是也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们也该告别了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长久以来承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话至今为止的努力便没有意义了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后任何事都必须一个人去做了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「没问题」这句话就是这意思是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望务必能够谅解是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要照我们所教的去做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便没有问题是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又和天壤之劫火在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无须担心了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(没问题)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比鲁海尔米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没我看着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜食也不可以吃得太多…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望紧紧拥抱你是也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那么喜欢吃蜜瓜包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算啥
